    "description": "<p>After you finish @UUID[Compendium.fu-azure-compendia.effects.LOyDXg3cySJFVbK4]{Channeling} you summon a great meteor from the heavens above the battlefield which will will crash at the <strong>end of the next round</strong>. Unless stopped, it will deal <strong>massive fire damage</strong> to all your targets. Enduring the meteor is an <strong>6-secction clock</strong> they must attempt to erase.</p><p>At the <strong>end of the next round</strong> each of your targets may attempt to turn back the clock with a <strong>suitable hard check</strong>.</p><table><tbody><tr><td data-colwidth=\"383\"><p><strong>Clock Left</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Effect</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td data-colwidth=\"383\"><p>Full</p></td><td><p>All targets suffer @DMG[999 fire]</p></td></tr><tr><td data-colwidth=\"383\"><p>Half</p></td><td><p>All targets suffer @DMG[$massive fire]</p></td></tr><tr><td data-colwidth=\"383\"><p>Empty</p></td><td><p>All targets gain @UUID[Compendium.fu-azure-compendia.effects.Item.hnXVEabmOmtGQtNv]{Brilliant Conviction} for 1 round</p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
